Class LancerGyro

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.parsing.IDevice, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.parsing.ISensor, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.PIDSource

    public class LancerGyro
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Gyro
    An add-on to the original gyro class to include temperature compensation and and to simply read out the temperature on the gyro. This gyro class is meant for the ADXRS652BBGZ-RL - Gyro which came in the FRC 2012 KOP.
    Author:
    Eric
